sql:
SELECT title, ingredients
FROM recipes
WHERE recipe_id = 1;

SELECT AVG(cooking_time) AS average_cooking_time
FROM recipes
WHERE total_time > 60 AND published = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "Shining stars of the culinary world" metaphorically refers to the best-rated recipes;
- "Captured the hearts and votes" signifies recipes with high average ratings and a significant number of helpful votes;
- "Cumulative support from the community" is a metaphor for the total number of helpful votes received.
